nt discount through membership to Xbox Game Pass, meaning that players do not have to bid farewell to their progress in these games. </p><figure id="attachment_3516557" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3516557" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3516557" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/dead-space-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-later-this-month-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3516557" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Like A Dragon: Ishin&#39; Credit: Sega</figcaption></figure><p> Regarding for the new lot of titles, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/like-a-dragon-ishin"><em>Like A Dragon: Ishin</em></a> is playable today (October 17). In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/like-a-dragon-ishin-review-3398207"><em>NME</em> &#39;s review of the game</a> , the historical spin-off earned praise for its bustling set pieces as well as its enthralling story, balanced with the series&#39; penchant for some silliness.</p><p> “Whether you&#39;re looking for a gritty tale of revenge or just want to knock back sake and belt your heart out at karaoke, Kyo has it all – and it&#