xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> versions of the game in the interest of quality.</p><p> A few days ahead of Halloween, <em>Dead Space</em> will come to the subscription service on cloud, console and PC on October 26.</p><p> However, this is only playable for those who pay for Xbox Game Pass Ultimate which bundles a selection of <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">Electronic Arts</a> titles in with bonuses like exclusive discounts and in-game content.</p><p> Also arriving on October 26 are <em>Frog Detective: The Entire Mystery</em> and <em>Mineko&#39;s Night Market</em> . Last but by no means least, <em>Headbangers: Rhythm Royale</em> and <em>Jusant</em> will become available through cloud, console and PC on October 31.</p><p> In other gaming news, it was announced that <em>Cities: Skylines 2</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cities-skylines-2-will-not-use-steam-workshop-for-mods-3516501">will not use Steam Workshop to support its mods</a> in order that the PC and console players are on a level playing field.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-game-pass-gets-dead-space-and-cities-skylines-2-this-month-3516535">Xbox Game Pass gets &#39;Dead Space&#39; and &#39;Cities: Skylines 2&#39; this month</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
